Interface:
- User can submit and register an account
- User can log in
- User can delete account

User class
  - attributes => name, password
  - user signs up/logs in
  - has a win score
  - has a lose score
  - has a total games score
  - has a win streak score

User controller and views
  - '/signup' => renders sign up form
  - '/signup' => processes sign up form, creates user, post
  - '/login' => renders login form
  - '/login' => processes login form, post
  - need to set sessions
  - user can view their stats, 'user/:id/stats'

Stats class
  - attributes => name, value
  - stats belong to user

Where to start?
- Set upp classes
- Set up my database
- Users controller